snippet.title: Madtale Pre-Registration Now Live!
snippet.description:
Pre-Register now: https://madtale.onelink.me/M9Nm/c0yu0l3b

Find the most unexpected ending in this DARK FAIRYTALE RPG!

Madtale is a time-saving and strategic idle RPG with a dark fairytale theme. You will enjoy thrilling rogue-like adventures, battle with enemies with the help of your unbeatable team, and get tremendous rewards effortlessly!
